    <br>
    <p class='tutoTXT'>
      RECIFS allows you to add specific points of interest to the map, so that you can estimate the environmental characteristics for these locations. <br><br>
      To add points of interest to the map, click on the Points of Interest button in the upper panel of the interface. 
    </p>
    <br>
    <button onclick='transitionTUTO7()'>OK</button>
