      <br><br>
      There are two ways of adding new points of interest: (1) via the interactive map or (2) from a .csv file containing the coordinates of the points of interest.
      <br><br>
      In this tutorial, you will use the interactive map method. 
      <br><br>
      Click on the <button style="background-color: #0f497e;">Add on map</button> button, then click on the map at the position where you want to add a point of interest. 
    </p>
    <br>
    <button onclick='transitionTUTO8()'>OK</button>
  </div>
</div>


