      <br><br>
      By default, all the "pre-computed variables" are available for download. 
      <br><br>
      If you want to download a custom variable created in the "advanced mode", you have to add it to the download list using the specific button (<img id='addDownF' style="width: 1cm; background-color: #0f497e;" src="public/buttons/buttonADD.svg" >), located in the top-left corner of the map.
      <br><br>
      Click on this button to add the variable shown on the map to the dowload list.    
    </p>
    <br>
    <button onclick='transitionTUTO9()'>OK</button>
  </div>
</div>


